            <p class="width2 vert-center">
                American Scripture Project is a national curriculum that cultivates civil discourse by using methods of religious text study to investigate historic American texts. The goal is to talk about big issues, unite over the shared experience of being American, and remind us that we are all in this democracy&nbsp;together.
            </p>
            <img src="assets/project-pages/s3_logoposter.jpg" alt="Poster highlighting logo" class="width6" id="S3">
